# NOTE: the SPA dist/ folder is intentionally allowed through. The prepackage hook in
# azure.yaml runs `npm run build` in src/Car.Tracker.Presentation/ to produce
# dist/, which the Dockerfile then copies into wwwroot/.
# Scoped re-include only to that exact path so we don't accidentally pull in
# unrelated "dist" folders from elsewhere.
!src/Car.Tracker.Presentation/dist
!src/Car.Tracker.Presentation/dist/**
